813
01:00:48,890 --> 01:00:52,020
It's not just him,
I have business with you, too.

814
01:00:52,150 --> 01:00:55,480
So it would be convenient to have
the both of you together.

815
01:01:12,040 --> 01:01:14,040
You want to kill Sakuma, don't you?

816
01:01:16,790 --> 01:01:18,090
I know you have a gun.

817
01:01:18,920 --> 01:01:20,510
It's purely precautionary.

818
01:01:20,970 --> 01:01:24,550
People used to call him
the Killing Machine.

819
01:01:24,680 --> 01:01:26,260
He's as quick as a snake.

820
01:01:26,760 --> 01:01:28,390
Come on, let's go!

821
01:01:40,480 --> 01:01:45,070
Tell Brother that Hagiwara's
here to see him.

822
01:02:31,740 --> 01:02:32,950
Mayumi!

823
01:02:40,800 --> 01:02:44,010
I didn't know he
was with the Medaka Family.

824
01:02:48,470 --> 01:02:50,890
Though I did think
he was probably a yakuza,

825
01:02:52,600 --> 01:02:54,850
what with the tattoo on his back.

826
01:02:59,980 --> 01:03:01,320
It's disgusting!

827
01:03:09,990 --> 01:03:11,780
You were like two beasts.

828
01:03:31,010 --> 01:03:33,810
The heroin that was meant for Fatso

829
01:03:35,430 --> 01:03:37,940
seems to have accidentally fallen
into the Medakas' hands.

830
01:03:40,690 --> 01:03:41,860
Please hand it over.

831
01:03:41,980 --> 01:03:43,110
I don't have it.

832
01:03:43,820 --> 01:03:46,030
- Give it back!
- I don't have the damn stuff!

833
01:03:46,150 --> 01:03:47,990
Fatso thinks you do.

834
01:03:50,160 --> 01:03:52,830
- If you don't cough it up...
- I want to see Fatso.

835
01:03:54,540 --> 01:03:55,700
Let me talk to him.

836
01:03:56,580 --> 01:03:57,830
He won't see you.

837
01:03:58,330 --> 01:03:59,620
Please, I'm asking you.

838
01:04:06,760 --> 01:04:07,880
Don't ask me.

839
01:04:08,470 --> 01:04:09,840
Ask your lady.

840
01:04:11,470 --> 01:04:12,510
Lady?

841
01:04:13,100 --> 01:04:15,310
The one you were just with, Brother.

842
01:04:21,980 --> 01:04:23,360
You don't know?

843
01:04:23,940 --> 01:04:26,610
She's Fatso's daughter.

844
01:04:29,780 --> 01:04:33,820
She's his only girl, but she ran away
because she couldn't stand him.

845
01:04:35,200 --> 01:04:38,040
If you bring her along,
maybe he'll see you.

846
01:04:40,080 --> 01:04:43,210
Otherwise, you better find that heroin.

847
01:04:44,000 --> 01:04:47,130
That's the only way
the Medaka Family is going to survive.

848
01:05:19,040 --> 01:05:20,500
I see.

849
01:05:21,290 --> 01:05:24,500
So she's this Mayumi you told me about.

850
01:05:26,250 --> 01:05:27,500
She's a fake.

851
01:05:28,840 --> 01:05:30,090
Most likely.

852
01:05:31,720 --> 01:05:35,760
I just picked her up at a bar I always
go to without thinking about it.

853
01:05:38,470 --> 01:05:40,270
She didn't tell you her name?

854
01:05:46,400 --> 01:05:50,360
Isn't that what most people do when they
meet someone for the first time?

855
01:05:54,280 --> 01:05:55,660
Most people, yeah.

856
01:05:57,780 --> 01:05:59,490
And you're not most people?

857
01:06:04,540 --> 01:06:06,710
I'm a yakuza. You know that.

858
01:06:11,090 --> 01:06:13,380
We might talk like we're all righteous,

859
01:06:15,340 --> 01:06:18,220
but we're rotten to the core.

860
01:06:21,640 --> 01:06:25,850
You can hardly bear
your own putrid stench.

861
01:06:28,110 --> 01:06:33,650
You have to deal with shit, and people,
even more rancid than yourself.

862
01:06:36,530 --> 01:06:41,830
